1
00:00:01,928 --> 00:00:05,881
Any guy who hurts Makino, will never get away from me.

2
00:00:06,862 --> 00:00:10,358
You should've said that way in the beginning.

3
00:00:10,359 --> 00:00:11,359
Huh?

4
00:00:11,660 --> 00:00:13,398
Domyouji Tower's Heliport.

5
00:00:13,399 --> 00:00:14,399
Eh?

6
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:15,589
Come right now.

7
00:00:15,590 --> 00:00:16,690
If you don't, I'll half-kill you..

8
00:00:17,591 --> 00:00:20,177
Papa has been laid-off!

9
00:00:20,178 --> 00:00:20,878
Eh?

10
00:00:20,879 --> 00:00:22,079
WHY?!?!?

11
00:00:27,919 --> 00:00:29,278
Papa..

12
00:00:29,679 --> 00:00:31,316
What do you mean by this?

13
00:00:31,417 --> 00:00:33,641
That's what I want to know..

14
00:00:34,142 --> 00:00:38,398
Umm..  This is a company owned house, right, Papa?

15
00:00:38,399 --> 00:00:41,540
Being laid off... Could it be?

16
00:00:41,541 --> 00:00:44,531
They said we have to leave by Christmas..

17
00:00:44,532 --> 00:00:45,432
Eh?

18
00:00:45,433 --> 00:00:46,767
Isn't that too soon?

19
00:00:46,768 --> 00:00:48,698
D*mnit..

20
00:00:48,899 --> 00:00:50,570
I'm desperate for Sake!

21
00:00:51,471 --> 00:00:52,150
Wai-

22
00:00:52,451 --> 00:00:53,437
Papa!

23
00:00:53,438 --> 00:00:54,438
Hey, calm down!

24
00:00:56,700 --> 00:00:59,909
D*mnit.  This beer has nothing but air coming out... D*mnit!

25
00:01:01,487 --> 00:01:03,791
You can just look for a new job, right?

26
00:01:03,792 --> 00:01:07,747
That's right!  
Let's just look towards the future! This isn't like you, Papa!

27
00:01:07,748 --> 00:01:08,925
Papa. Look!

28
00:01:08,926 --> 00:01:13,165
Today is special!  
It's okay for you to drink a new one! It's not much, but..

29
00:01:13,466 --> 00:01:15,166
Papa will do his best!

30
00:01:16,167 --> 00:01:18,375
Papa will definitely do his best!

31
00:01:27,792 --> 00:01:29,263
That witch.

32
00:01:33,702 --> 00:01:35,202
Saturn Being?

33
00:01:35,203 --> 00:01:36,501
Eh, who's the Saturn Being?

34
00:01:36,502 --> 00:01:37,496
Me and Makino.

35
00:01:37,497 --> 00:01:39,467
Saturn.. The one with the rings, that Saturn?

36
00:01:39,468 --> 00:01:40,513
I just told you that's the one!!

37
00:01:40,514 --> 00:01:42,614
Mercury, Venus, Earth, Mars, Jupiter, the dotted color Saturn!

38
00:01:42,615 --> 00:01:44,634
What dotted color?

39
00:01:44,635 --> 00:01:45,635
That's really funny!

40
00:01:46,905 --> 00:01:47,905
Anyway!

41
00:01:48,206 --> 00:01:51,178
Me and Makino are both Saturn beings, that's why,

42
00:01:51,179 --> 00:01:53,588
From the very beginning we are destined to be together.

43
00:01:53,589 --> 00:01:54,989
Is your brain okay?

44
00:01:56,531 --> 00:01:59,603
And I thought I'd go to the trouble of showing her our 
Native Planet..

45
00:01:59,604 --> 00:02:03,553
That peasant!  On top of ignoring me, she made me worry!

46
00:02:03,584 --> 00:02:05,252
Umm, you know what, Tsukasa-kun.

47
00:02:05,252 --> 00:02:08,111
We were born here on earth.. We're earthlings!!!

48
00:02:08,111 --> 00:02:10,119
No one was born in Saturn you know...

49
00:02:10,119 --> 00:02:11,440
Of course I know that!

50
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,107
Are you a baka (idiot)?

51
00:02:18,132 --> 00:02:19,658
No way.. Just now..

52
00:02:19,658 --> 00:02:21,871
Hanazawa Rui-san and my eyes met..

53
00:02:22,411 --> 00:02:23,508
He's coming over..

54
00:02:23,508 --> 00:02:24,970
Ooh, what should we do?

55
00:02:24,970 --> 00:02:27,344
Hey!
- Hai (yes)!

56
00:02:27,344 --> 00:02:28,651
Where's Makino?

57
00:02:28,651 --> 00:02:30,806
Makino-san, she's absent it seems..

58
00:02:30,806 --> 00:02:32,647
But I think she's just playing hooky~

59
00:02:34,591 --> 00:02:35,411
Oh no!

60
00:02:35,411 --> 00:02:38,045
Domyouji-san doing something like this!  I'm a little shocked!

61
00:02:38,045 --> 00:02:39,774
Do what you want, ugly!!

62
00:02:39,774 --> 00:02:41,683
Wait Tsukasa. Where are you going?

63
00:02:41,683 --> 00:02:44,049
Makino didn't show up, so I'm going home!

64
00:02:44,494 --> 00:02:46,013
Hai.

65
00:02:46,013 --> 00:02:47,936
Is that so?

66
00:02:47,936 --> 00:02:49,552
I understand.

67
00:02:49,552 --> 00:02:51,082
Excuse me.

68
00:02:58,174 --> 00:02:59,491
Planet fortune telling?

69
00:02:59,491 --> 00:03:01,247
Yeah, this one.

70
00:03:01,247 --> 00:03:02,984
Oh, so that's how it is, huh?

71
00:03:02,984 --> 00:03:04,036
It says here,

72
00:03:04,036 --> 00:03:06,378
both Tsukasa and Makino are Saturn Beings..

73
00:03:06,378 --> 00:03:09,257
And when you told Tsukasa about it..

74
00:03:09,257 --> 00:03:10,745
He was super happy!

75
00:03:10,745 --> 00:03:13,206
And that's why he thought he'd show Saturn to Makino!

76
00:03:13,206 --> 00:03:14,091
But..

77
00:03:14,091 --> 00:03:15,762
I wonder why Makino didn't come?

78
00:03:15,762 --> 00:03:17,414
It seems like she didn't even call.

79
00:03:17,414 --> 00:03:18,887
Should I call Yuuki-chan?

80
00:03:21,053 --> 00:03:22,251
Hello, Yuuki-chan?

81
00:03:22,251 --> 00:03:24,729
But you really like these kinds of things, Rui.

82
00:03:24,729 --> 00:03:25,978
Eh?

83
00:03:25,978 --> 00:03:26,989
Laid off?

84
00:03:26,989 --> 00:03:27,914
Hai.

85
00:03:27,914 --> 00:03:30,167
Her father has just been suddenly promoted,

86
00:03:30,167 --> 00:03:33,311
and the whole family were really happy..

87
00:03:33,311 --> 00:03:35,678
That aside, why do you look so happy?

88
00:03:36,094 --> 00:03:37,465
Uh no..

89
00:03:37,865 --> 00:03:40,805
I thought I'd give Nishikado-san a call.. but..

90
00:03:40,805 --> 00:03:45,156
I didn't have any courage after all.. I was feeling really down..

91
00:03:45,156 --> 00:03:46,471
I didn't expect Nishikado-san to-

92
00:03:46,471 --> 00:03:48,758
But, it's a real pity..

93
00:03:48,758 --> 00:03:51,830
They were already that poor.. Then being laid-off..

94
00:03:51,830 --> 00:03:54,629
After all, are you just playing me around, Nishikado-san?

95
00:03:58,202 --> 00:04:01,635
That's Tsukasa's mom's work, isn't it?

96
00:04:02,118 --> 00:04:03,524
Umm..

97
00:04:03,524 --> 00:04:06,527
The same thing happened with Tsukasa's Oneesan..

98
00:04:11,715 --> 00:04:14,063
Recently,

99
00:04:14,691 --> 00:04:16,721
it's been really rare..

100
00:04:16,721 --> 00:04:19,202
Eating here at home..

101
00:04:24,238 --> 00:04:25,904
Is that suppose to be me?

102
00:04:25,904 --> 00:04:28,022
Or is it you?

103
00:04:32,613 --> 00:04:35,130
When are you going back?

104
00:04:39,975 --> 00:04:41,783
Just go back already.

105
00:04:42,761 --> 00:04:47,041
When everything goes my way..  
I will immediately go back to New York.

106
00:04:48,556 --> 00:04:50,529
When every piece falls into place.

107
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:57,623
5 million yen? (about $41,480)

108
00:04:57,623 --> 00:04:59,238
There must've been some mistake?

109
00:04:59,238 --> 00:05:01,057
This is the loan proof, Ojou-san (young lady or daughter, honorable)

110
00:05:01,057 --> 00:05:02,237
Please!!

111
00:05:02,237 --> 00:05:04,793
Can you just please wait a bit more?

112
00:05:04,793 --> 00:05:08,060
Well, you've been laid-off, right Otochan (father)?

113
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:09,291
Huh?!

114
00:05:09,291 --> 00:05:11,677
But, I'll find a job soon, and work hard..

115
00:05:11,677 --> 00:05:14,379
Everyone is doing the same thing, stupid!

116
00:05:14,379 --> 00:05:16,019
Even if you say "Find a job right now..".  It's..

117
00:05:16,019 --> 00:05:18,627
10 days, I'll give you 10 days.

118
00:05:18,627 --> 00:05:23,413
There are really some stingy people in this world..

119
00:05:40,718 --> 00:05:42,312
Excuse me..

120
00:05:50,195 --> 00:05:52,485
Makino Tsukushi just submitted a leave of absence!

121
00:05:54,901 --> 00:05:57,591
I think she's finally not able to pay her tuition fee, right?

122
00:05:57,591 --> 00:05:59,523
At this rate, she'll have to quit school for sure!

123
00:05:59,523 --> 00:06:02,362
Awesome, that'll be soo great!

124
00:06:03,814 --> 00:06:05,031
Are they serious?

125
00:06:05,031 --> 00:06:07,400
After last night's talk with Yuuki-chan..

126
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:10,199
Dropping out of school..
It's not an impossible story, right?

127
00:06:10,199 --> 00:06:12,964
It's really Tsukasa's Mother's work, after all..

128
00:06:12,964 --> 00:06:14,281
Well, we don't know that yet.

129
00:06:28,065 --> 00:06:30,225
What are we going to do?

130
00:06:30,225 --> 00:06:34,813
On top of being laid off, we have a 5 million yen debt..

131
00:06:34,813 --> 00:06:37,348
It wasn't like that at first...

132
00:06:37,348 --> 00:06:39,815
I borrowed, thinking I can pay it off by my next bonus..

133
00:06:39,815 --> 00:06:43,848
You say that, but you were just betting on Horse Racing, right?

134
00:06:43,848 --> 00:06:45,279
I'm sorry.

135
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:49,461
Especially at times like these..

136
00:06:49,461 --> 00:06:52,604
Let's combine our strengths and do our best!

137
00:06:53,556 --> 00:06:55,208
Tsukushi!!

138
00:06:58,913 --> 00:07:01,076
Let's look upwards and walk!

139
00:07:09,149 --> 00:07:10,334
- Hanazawa Rui -

140
00:07:11,213 --> 00:07:12,429
Uh.. why?

141
00:07:14,006 --> 00:07:16,090
Looks like things are pretty bad..

142
00:07:16,090 --> 00:07:17,748
Eh?

143
00:07:18,725 --> 00:07:21,770
Yeah, but it's totally okay, you know.

144
00:07:21,770 --> 00:07:25,374
I wanted to talk to you about something.
- Eh?

145
00:07:25,374 --> 00:07:27,635
Right now, where are you?

146
00:07:27,635 --> 00:07:31,218
Ikebukoro's West Gate Park..

147
00:07:31,218 --> 00:07:33,057
'Sup! Makino,

148
00:07:33,057 --> 00:07:34,755
did she come in today?

149
00:07:34,755 --> 00:07:35,536
Nope.

150
00:07:35,536 --> 00:07:38,372
Makino just submitted a leave of absence.

151
00:07:38,372 --> 00:07:39,020
Eh?

152
00:07:40,847 --> 00:07:42,685
He's late..

153
00:07:46,732 --> 00:07:48,049
Whoa-

154
00:07:48,049 --> 00:07:50,294
This is a good place..
- Hey. Hey. Hey.

155
00:07:50,294 --> 00:07:52,314
You're an Eitoku Ojousan, right?

156
00:07:52,314 --> 00:07:54,214
Looking for a part time job?

157
00:07:55,570 --> 00:07:57,358
Please excuse me.

158
00:07:57,358 --> 00:07:59,723
It's a really awesome part time job!

159
00:08:00,164 --> 00:08:03,708
We'll just take a little picture of you in your uniform, and you'll get.

160
00:08:03,708 --> 00:08:05,400
100,000 yen ($828)!

161
00:08:07,546 --> 00:08:08,697
Seriously??

162
00:08:08,697 --> 00:08:10,200
I was just thinking,

163
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,445
but I think your Mom-
-Did you hear?

164
00:08:12,445 --> 00:08:13,950
Tsukushi-chan..

165
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:16,319
seems to be really in trouble..

166
00:08:18,067 --> 00:08:19,143
It's really great!

167
00:08:19,143 --> 00:08:23,259
Let's just take a few pictures.. a few pictures, okay?
Right here, right here..

168
00:08:25,522 --> 00:08:27,122
It'll be great!

169
00:08:30,512 --> 00:08:31,928
Hey you!

170
00:08:31,928 --> 00:08:33,761
It's your doing again, huh?

171
00:08:33,761 --> 00:08:34,976
I really don't know anything at all.

172
00:08:34,976 --> 00:08:35,913
You liar!!

173
00:08:35,913 --> 00:08:38,417
When things happen to Makino,
Surely you're involved in it!

174
00:08:38,417 --> 00:08:39,418
I swear, this time..

175
00:08:39,418 --> 00:08:41,865
Your mother has never asked me to do anything..

176
00:08:41,865 --> 00:08:43,019
Huh?

177
00:08:46,402 --> 00:08:48,360
You..

178
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:51,314
You've been conspiring with my "BABA" (old woman, hag)?

179
00:08:51,314 --> 00:08:52,471
but..

180
00:08:52,471 --> 00:08:53,711
With my own will..

181
00:08:53,711 --> 00:08:56,463
I really wanted to be with you..

182
00:08:58,057 --> 00:08:59,495
No!!

183
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:02,207
Will you behave?

184
00:09:02,637 --> 00:09:06,828
If you just take your clothes.. You'll get 100,000.

185
00:09:06,828 --> 00:09:09,016
You said it's just a picture of me in my uniform..

186
00:09:09,016 --> 00:09:12,638
They say for every sweet deal, there's a back side.

187
00:09:13,540 --> 00:09:14,774
Don't come!

188
00:09:14,774 --> 00:09:16,210
Don't go any closer!!

189
00:09:16,210 --> 00:09:18,973
The back side is the back side.  And a back side video!

190
00:09:18,973 --> 00:09:20,362
Stop it!!!!

191
00:09:20,362 --> 00:09:21,660
Hana Yori Dango

