We're running for it!

210
00:12:08,577 --> 00:12:09,747
Nee-chan.

211
00:12:11,454 --> 00:12:13,370
Can you lend me your strength for a bit?

212
00:12:20,385 --> 00:12:21,597
I've been..

213
00:12:21,597 --> 00:12:24,220
saved by Hanazawa Rui again..

214
00:12:28,721 --> 00:12:30,120
Thank you.

215
00:12:32,365 --> 00:12:33,810
You didn't talk to Tsukasa,

216
00:12:34,610 --> 00:12:40,104
about the situation with your dad and your leave of absence?

217
00:12:40,676 --> 00:12:41,728
Yeah.

218
00:12:43,777 --> 00:12:46,818
Coz' you don't want to unnecessarily let him worry?

219
00:12:47,888 --> 00:12:51,336
No, that's not the reason why, or should I say...

220
00:12:52,032 --> 00:12:54,673
It's possible,

221
00:12:54,673 --> 00:12:58,151
that Tsukasa's mother is the one moving behind the scenes..

222
00:13:01,908 --> 00:13:03,333
It can't be..

223
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:07,711
That person is an Iron Woman after all..

224
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:11,993
Even so, no matter what, that's just too-

225
00:13:11,993 --> 00:13:13,359
No.

226
00:13:14,097 --> 00:13:17,110
If there's something to do, 
she's a person who will do it completely and thoroughly.

227
00:13:23,572 --> 00:13:25,870
Don't try to shoulder everything on your own..

228
00:13:25,870 --> 00:13:28,763
If something happens, you can always come to me for help.

229
00:13:30,259 --> 00:13:31,821
Thank you.

230
00:13:39,848 --> 00:13:42,041
Iron Woman, huh?

231
00:13:42,582 --> 00:13:43,965
Could it be, that is -

232
00:13:43,965 --> 00:13:45,685
Who is?

233
00:13:45,685 --> 00:13:48,180
Me? I'm an Iron Woman?

234
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:51,462
Uh no.  It's not you..

235
00:13:54,062 --> 00:13:55,468
Umm..

236
00:13:55,468 --> 00:14:00,922
Among the men you once loved.  Was there a parent who will not
care about the means just for the sake of his beloved son?

237
00:14:00,922 --> 00:14:02,591
Ahh, it's the inverse of the usual pattern..

238
00:14:02,591 --> 00:14:04,311
Now that you mention, there is..

239
00:14:04,311 --> 00:14:05,930
a troublesome man...

240
00:14:05,930 --> 00:14:07,229
Ahh, bingo!

241
00:14:07,229 --> 00:14:08,842
What kind of person was he?

242
00:14:08,842 --> 00:14:11,585
Decisively, a woman of the polar!

243
00:14:11,586 --> 00:14:12,786
Otsu (strange, queer)

244
00:14:13,803 --> 00:14:16,531
She was a woman who raised him by herself.

245
00:14:16,531 --> 00:14:18,982
And at the time that I was introduced to her..

246
00:14:18,982 --> 00:14:20,787
She started getting angry, and she was like a fire...

247
00:14:20,787 --> 00:14:21,491
Prepare yourself!!

248
00:14:21,491 --> 00:14:24,846
But the two of us stubbornly opposed her!

249
00:14:24,846 --> 00:14:27,180
And at that time, we gained our happiness!

250
00:14:27,180 --> 00:14:29,080
Don't under estimate me!!!

251
00:14:30,402 --> 00:14:31,836
After that..?

252
00:14:33,318 --> 00:14:35,639
At the time when I wasn't aware...

253
00:14:35,639 --> 00:14:39,528
I was somehow thrown out by that mother's hands..

254
00:14:39,528 --> 00:14:40,933
And that was the end..

255
00:14:43,242 --> 00:14:44,664
Ah, by the way!

256
00:14:44,664 --> 00:14:47,617
Tsukushi-chan, I forgot..

257
00:14:47,617 --> 00:14:49,972
Here, it's not much, but..

258
00:14:50,412 --> 00:14:51,720
What is it?

259
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,925
I heard you're having quite some problems?

260
00:14:56,481 --> 00:14:58,042
Uh, no.. It's fine..

261
00:14:58,042 --> 00:14:59,728
It's really not much.

262
00:14:59,728 --> 00:15:00,519
Uh, but..

263
00:15:00,519 --> 00:15:05,874
Once your father gets a job, and everything calms down, 
you can just properly pay me then..

264
00:15:06,395 --> 00:15:07,960
Kami-san..

265
00:15:08,595 --> 00:15:10,716
Everyone's with you, you know..

266
00:15:10,716 --> 00:15:14,402
